Listening to my dad.

00:11:09.840 --> 00:11:11.470
We all grew up in Kalapana.

00:11:11.470 --> 00:11:15.250
Yeah, as we were young, that's
all we hear every day and listen

00:11:15.250 --> 00:11:17.750
