00:14:11.100 --> 00:14:16.340
Especially some of us we
hear this music and it kind

00:14:16.340 --> 00:14:18.870
of heals, the music heals.

00:14:18.870 --> 00:14:21.050
So, we felt -- I just fell in love.

00:14:21.050 --> 00:14:26.360
And the more I hear it the
more I want to do it, so.

00:14:26.360 --> 00:14:30.290
&gt;&gt;JOHN FENN: So, it's not
necessarily a set of tunings are --

00:14:30.290 --> 00:14:33.390
