don't want to tap,

00:20:30.070 --> 00:20:31.390
we just want to play
the way you play.

00:20:31.390 --> 00:20:32.690
I said, "Okay."

00:20:32.690 --> 00:20:36.240
Then just sort of do the
video and help them, yeah.

00:20:36.240 --> 00:20:41.650
&gt;&gt;JOHN FENN: Are you finding
that there's young players

00:20:41.650 --> 00:20:44.160
who are wanting to learn slack key?

00:20:44.160 --> 00:20:47.150
