teacher is go, you know, reading.

00:23:52.710 --> 00:23:57.680
I play my horn and the next thing
I hear these notes in my head,

00:23:57.680 --> 00:24:00.900
and look at the song, hear
the notes and I just play on.

00:24:00.900 --> 00:24:03.840
And the band teacher stops
the whole class, stop, stop.

00:24:03.840 --> 00:24:05.160 position:56%
He looks at me, goes, "Mr. Kaapana?"

00:24:05.160 --> 00:24:06.460
I say, "yes."

00:24:06.460 --> 00:24:09.330
He goes, "What's that
note on your music sheet?"

00:24:09.330 --> 00:24:11.950
And I go, "It's not there."

00:24:11.950 --> 00:24:14.800
And he goes, "Play the
notes on the sheet."

00:24:14.800 --> 00:24:20.030
Okay. I play the note
