what that is?"

00:24:42.020 --> 00:24:44.370
I said, "Nope."

00:24:44.370 --> 00:24:48.750
He said, "That's gifted."

00:24:48.750 --> 00:24:50.070
Oh, thank you.

00:24:50.070 --> 00:24:54.610
after that, that's why I didn't
read notes, I just play it.

00:24:54.610 --> 00:24:56.420
he goes like that, he smiles.

