00:25:19.430 --> 00:25:24.640
because they don't read notes in
Kalapana, He's always pressing

00:25:24.640 --> 00:25:29.500
on his guitar, so he said, when
I asked him what he's' doing,

00:25:29.500 --> 00:25:31.840
he looks at me, he
don't know what key,

00:25:31.840 --> 00:25:34.690
he just looks at me,
tell me, "Just press."

00:25:34.690 --> 00:25:35.990
I said, "What?"

00:25:35.990 --> 00:25:37.290
yeah, just press.

00:25:37.290 --> 00:25:38.620
So, I start pressing
and he looks at me

00:25:38.620 --> 00:25:43.390
and he tells me, "Press
the right key."

00:25:43.390 --> 00:25:45.040
&gt;&gt;JOHN FENN: So there's some
learning with that step.

00:25:45.040 --> 00:25:46.460
&gt;&gt;LEDWARD KAAPANA:
yeah, yeah, yeah, yeah.

00:25:46.460 --> 00:25:49.240
So, that's where Just
Press came from.

00:25:49.240 --> 00:25:50.540
Yep.

00:25:50.540 --> 00:25:54.760 position:56%
