&gt;&gt;LEDWARD KAAPANA: Yes.

00:29:16.680 --> 00:29:17.980
&gt;&gt;JOHN FENN: You know,
people from --

00:29:17.980 --> 00:29:22.210
&gt;&gt;LEDWARD KAAPANA: I did I
