&gt;&gt;LEDWARD KAAPANA: teach
that -- yeah, I got songbird,

00:40:27.880 --> 00:40:31.740
got actually -- yeah, electric.

00:40:31.740 --> 00:40:35.270
Like playing the electric
typewriter.

